Package se.ju23.typespeeder.consle

Class Console

java.lang.Object
se.ju23.typespeeder.consle.Console
@Component public class Console extends Object
Version:
1.0.0 since 2024-02-08

Console

the Console class print out all the text in a console. If a language is given the Console will print out in the given language.

Author:
Sofie Van Dingenen
